reviewText:
This film is amazing in a so-bad-it's-excellent way. Inspired by Miami Connection, this film manages to be absurd and delightful at once. We have been making everyone watch it, and are planning a viewing party with themed cocktails.

Easily the best viewing experience I've paid for on Amazon!
Best lesbian action film ever! I especially love the prison scene. If you love John Waters you will love this! I highly recommend this film. It's very funny and cute.

SPOILERS?

Dyke Hard is a band made from misfits. The lead singer opts out of the band and frames the rest of the band for murder. The film ends with a battle of the bands.

The movie is campy with bad musical numbers.

Guide: Sex and nudity (male and female )
